snippet.title: Carnal Instinct - Announcement Trailer
snippet.description:
Carnal Instinct is an Adult RPG with an emphasis on AAA quality visuals, engaging narrative, and compelling erotic interaction. Our initial playable release is scheduled for 11.11.2020.

Like what you see? Find out more or support development at https://www.patreon.com/carnal_instinct
